<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .logo-area {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px 0 10px;
      }
      .logo-area img {
        width: 80px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .brand-text {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #e87722;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 24px 32px;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #1a1a1a;
        font-size: 17px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 6px 0;
      }
      .credentials-box {
        background: #fff3e0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        margin: 18px 0;
      }
      .credentials-box p {
        margin: 4px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .btn-wrap {
        margin: 24px 0 10px;
      }
      .link-fallback {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #555;
        margin-top: 12px;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .link-fallback a {
        color: #3177ff;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 14px;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #999;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">

      <!-- Logo -->
      <div class="logo-area">
        <img src="cid:govishop_logo" alt="GoViShop" />
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to GoViShop – Your Standard Plan is Activated</h2>

        <p>Dear <strong>{{supplierName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Warm greetings from GoViShop!</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your
          <strong>Standard Plan</strong>
          has been successfully activated, and your account has been created.</p>
        <p>Welcome to the GoViShop community! You can now start exploring our
          platform and enjoy the features available under your plan.</p>
        <p>Your login details are as follows:</p>

        <div class="credentials-box">
          <p>Username: <strong>{{contact}} / {{email}}</strong></p>
          <p>Temporary Password: <strong>{{tempPassword}}</strong></p>
        </div>

        <p>For security reasons, we strongly recommend that you change your
          password after your first login.</p>
        <p>To get started, simply log in using the link below:</p>

        <!-- ── Gradient Login Button ── -->
        <div class="btn-wrap">

          <a
            href="{{loginUrl}}"
            style="
             background: linear-gradient(to right, #F97316, #FF9829);
             color: #ffffff;
             text-decoration: none;
             padding: 14px 0;
             border-radius: 6px;
             font-size: 15px;
             font-weight: bold;
             display: block;
             text-align: center;
             width: 100%;
             box-sizing: border-box;
           "
          >
            Login
          </a>
          <!--<![endif]-->
        </div>

        <p class="link-fallback">
          If the button doesn't work, copy and paste the link into your browser:<br
          />
          <a href="{{loginUrl}}">{{loginUrl}}</a>
        </p>

        <br />
        <p>Thank you,</p>
        <p><strong>GoViShop Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        ©
        {{year}}
        Polygon Holdings Limited. All Rights Reserved.<br />
        Please note that this is an automated message.
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>